    "\"Defining Virtual Reality: Dimensions Determining Telepresence\", by Steuer (1992), with six citations.",
    "This paper explores the concept of VR and identifies key dimensions that contribute to the sense of telepresence within virtual environments.",
    "It has also been analyzed the link strength of each publication.",
    "Link strength indicates the total strength of the links of an item with other items (van Eck and Waltman 2022).",
    "Following this measure, there are different results."
